g.title: assert(!options.app[options.name], `${options.name} is already exists in app`)
assert(!(options.client && options.clients), `egg:singleton ${this.name} can not set options.client and options.clients both`)
assert(!(options.client && options.clients), `egg:singleton ${this.name} can not set options.client and options.clients both`)
